      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Ãšrn is a Bundingsteinn diver &mdash; one of the coastal kinship specialists who navigate the flooded reef-caves and drowned passages beneath the Singing Islands shelf. He is compact and strong-necked, with calluses on both palms from years of pulling through current. He smells of brine regardless of how long he has been ashore.</p><p>He hires out as a guide to the drowned sections. He knows the tides better than the moons do, he says. This is almost true.</p>",
